## 2 · Spawn order

### Greenfield

1. Admin provides path map → spawn **Master Pool Lead** (`MASTER-POOL-LEAD-PROMPT.md`)  
2. Lead stops at **awaiting Admin pool lock** (roster + paths filled)  
3. Admin locks → status `admin-locked` / `active`  
4. Brains and working teams may run per pool prompts  

### Per Research Brain pass

1. Paste `pools/<id>/BRAIN-PROMPT.md` into a fresh agent (or resume Brain session)  
2. Brain appends HIGHLIGHTS / DIGESTS; may append PROPOSALS; escalates only `interesting` / `important` → `INBOX.md`  
3. Stop for Admin review on escalations — no auto WORKSTREAMS rows  

### Per shipping unit (delegates to build-master)

Use the product’s Master Build Orchestrator / Build / Audit prompts — **not** this pack’s Lead. Pool `TEAMS.md` may deep-link those prompts.

